 Introduction:
 
 Pragyan CMS is a multi user based cms to organize & facilitate collaborative 
 content creation & updation on a website, written in PHP and MySql. It 
 provides tools to manage permissions for users and groups and modules like 
 article, form, quiz, forums etc.Pragyan CMS is used to handle the creation, 
 updation and administration of a website.
 
