 Features:

  * Multi-user open source content management system
  * Used to organize and facilitate collaborative content creation and updation
  * Handy tools to manage permissions for groups and users
  * Quickly create pages of type article, gallery, quiz, form and forum
  * Template installation module with compatibility check
  * Have page-specific templates so every page can have its own template
  * Easily convert pages into PDF
  * Google Maps and Latex plugin in pages of type articles
  * Powerful search engine powered by Sphider
  * Send mass emails to site registrants
  * Security and protection against hacking attempts ( like XSS and Injections )
  
 Requirements:
 
    php 5.2.4 or later
    MySQL 5.0.45 or later
    a javascript and cookies enabled web-browser (duh!)
    
 Download:
 
    You can get the latest version at http://sourceforge.net/projects/pragyan

